We can use fleets to destroy system-based units, including garrisons.  To order an orbital bombardment, move a fleet to the planet you wish to bombard; once the fleet has arrived at its destination, right-click on the fleet, and select 'Orbital Bombardment' from the pop-up menu.  There are three types of orbital bombardments available to us: General, Military, and Civilian.  I must caution you, however, that the population may turn against us if we destroy non-military targets.